      <title>特朗普顾问寻求重塑美联储领导层</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/trump-advisers-look-to-reshape-fed-leadership-as-roles-open</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，当选总统唐纳德·特朗普的顾问正在考虑如何重塑美联储的领导层，包括提升美联储理事米歇尔·鲍曼为央行下一任监管副主席。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/trump-advisers-look-to-reshape-fed-leadership-as-roles-open</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 16:41:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
